-- Merkel, Draghi to Meet in Berlin on Sept. 25, Spokesman Says
-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 2012-09-20T14:59:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-20/merkel-draghi-to-meet-in-berlin-on-sept-25-spokesman-says.html
German Chancellor Angela Merkel and
European Central Bank President  Mario Draghi  will meet in Berlin
on Sept. 25, a German government spokesman said.  The meeting will take place at Merkel’s chancellery,
Steffen Seibert, her chief spokesman, said in a text message.  Merkel and Draghi are due to speak separately the same day
at a conference in Berlin organized by Germany’s BDI industrial
lobby group.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tony Czuczka in Berlin at 
 aczuczka@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at 
 jhertling@bloomberg.net  